🌐 Shodan & Censys (Professional Recon Tools)

Both Shodan and Censys are powerful platforms used in active reconnaissance to discover internet-facing assets like servers, IoT devices, and services.

👉 Think of them as:

Google → searches websites
Shodan/Censys → 🔥 search the entire internet infrastructure
--------------------------------------------------------------------

🔍 What is Shodan?

Shodan scans the internet and indexes:

Open ports
Running services
Devices (cameras, routers, servers)
✅ What You Can Find:
Exposed databases
Open RDP/SSH ports
IoT devices (CCTV, webcams)
Misconfigured servers

---------------------------------------------------------------------

🔍 What is Censys?

Censys is more research-focused and provides:

Deep SSL/TLS data
Certificate analysis
Internet-wide scanning datasets

👉 Used heavily by:

Security researchers
Blue teams
Threat intelligence analysts

---------------------------------------------------------------------

| Feature      | Shodan     | Censys            |
| ------------ | ---------- | ----------------- |
| Ease of Use  | Easy       | Moderate          |
| Data Depth   | Medium     | Deep 🔥           |
| SSL Analysis | Basic      | Advanced          |
| UI           | Simple     | Technical         |
