🔎 Censys Queries (Advanced Search)

🎯 Find HTTPS Services
services.service_name: HTTP

🔐 Find SSL Certificates
services.tls.certificates.leaf_data.subject.common_name: example.com

🌐 Find Domain Assets
example.com

🔎 Filter by Port
services.port: 443

Good for: expired certs, misconfigured https, leaked subdomains

